717790f-a.title: Manhattan: Broadway - 192nd Street
717790f-a.text:
(1)
Broadway, west.side, between 192nd Street and Bennett Avenue,
showing work on the Eighth Avenue subway.  October 26, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
No REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
